---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout
	title="PYRS Docs | Getting Started"
	description="User-facing PYRS documentation for install, quickstart, and core usage."
	active="docs"
>
	<section class="page-hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">Documentation</p>
		<h1>Get productive with PYRS quickly.</h1>
		<p class="lede">
			This is the user-facing docs surface for installation, first-run workflow, and runtime usage.
			Reference details live in the dedicated reference pages.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="link-grid">
		<a class="link-card" href="/#install">
			<h2>Install</h2>
			<p>Use MacOS/Linux install commands with Cargo, Docker, or nightly archives.</p>
		</a>
		<a class="link-card" href="/reference/">
			<h2>Reference</h2>
			<p>CLI modes, startup flags, and environment variables from the current implementation.</p>
		</a>
		<a class="link-card" href="https://github.com/BlueBlazin/pyrs">
			<h2>Repository</h2>
			<p>Track releases, CI status, issues, and implementation updates directly on GitHub.</p>
		</a>
	</section>

	<section class="doc-section">
		<h2>Quickstart</h2>
		<p class="section-lede">Install from GitHub and verify your runtime is available.</p>
		<pre><code>cargo install --locked --git https://github.com/BlueBlazin/pyrs --bin pyrs
pyrs --version
pyrs
pyrs -c "import sys; print(sys.version)"</code></pre>
	</section>

	<section class="doc-section">
		<h2>Core Workflow</h2>
		<div class="checklist">
			<div class="check-item">
				<h3>Run source files</h3>
				<p>Execute Python source directly with `pyrs path/to/script.py`.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="check-item">
				<h3>Run CPython bytecode</h3>
				<p>Execute `.pyc` files with `pyrs path/to/module.pyc`.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="check-item">
				<h3>Interactive REPL</h3>
				<p>Use `pyrs` with syntax highlighting, multiline input, and expression echo.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
	.page-hero {
		padding: 0.6rem 0 0.2rem;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		color: var(--accent-2);
		letter-spacing: 0.09em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.76rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.7rem);
		line-height: 1.08;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.lede {
		margin: 0.92rem 0 0;
		max-width: 66ch;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.58;
	}

	.link-grid {
		margin-top: 1.35rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.86rem;
	}

	.link-card {
		display: block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 0.92rem;
		padding: 0.88rem 0.95rem;
		transition: transform 120ms ease, border-color 120ms ease, box-shadow 120ms ease;
	}

	.link-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-1px);
		border-color: #6a4432;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.link-card h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.02rem;
	}

	.link-card p {
		margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.doc-section {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.06rem;
		border-radius: 0.92rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		background: rgba(18, 12, 10, 0.7);
	}

	.doc-section h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.section-lede {
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	pre {
		margin: 0.82rem 0 0;
		overflow-x: auto;
		padding: 0.82rem 0.92rem;
		border-radius: 0.76rem;
		border: 1px solid #3f2a1f;
		background: #080605;
		color: #ecd9cd;
		font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		line-height: 1.56;
	}

	.checklist {
		margin-top: 0.85rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.7rem;
	}

	.check-item {
		padding: 0.78rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 0.76rem;
		border: 1px solid #3f2b20;
		background: rgba(10, 8, 7, 0.72);
	}

	.check-item h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.check-item p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.87rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 960px) {
		.link-grid,
		.checklist {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
